td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Articles 63, 167, 168, 178 to 180, 182 and 219 of Council Directive 2006/112/EC of 28 November 2006 on the common system of value added tax (
OJ 2006 L 347, p. 1
) (‘the VAT Directive’) and also of the principle of fiscal neutrality.
